node.text: We’ve put together a quick survey to give you all a chance to share your thoughts about Rifle Paper Co. and what you’re looking for from us. We would love to hear from you! 💕 Find the survey at the link in our bio, and as a thank you, there is a 15% off code at the end. #riflepaperco
